attrs.name: Police, protesters clash in Ferguson over teen's death

contents.caption: Police advance through smoke in Ferguson, Mo. The St. Louis suburb has been rocked by racial unrest since a white police officer shot an unarmed black teenager to death. Protests turned violent with people lobbing Molotov cocktails at police, who responded with smoke bombs and tear gas to disperse the crowd.
contents.headline: Police, protesters clash in Ferguson over teen's death

attrs.name: caption
attrs.value: Police advance through smoke, Wednesday, Aug. 13, 2014, in Ferguson, Mo.  Protests in the St. Louis suburb rocked by racial unrest since a white police officer shot an unarmed black teenager to death turned violent Wednesday night, with people lobbing molotov cocktails at police who responded with smoke bombs and tear gas to disperse the crowd.  (AP Photo/Jeff Roberson)  ORG XMIT: MOJR126
